issues.title: New TorBrowser provokes ZeroHello warning in Tor Always Enabled mode.
issues.body:
Torbrowser version:
8.5 (based on Mozilla Firefox 60.7.0esr) (64-bit), running in safest security level, on windows platform

Warning: "Your Browser is not safe.  To protect your anonymity you should use ZeroNet in the Tor Browser. [Restart Zeronet Client]"
